<h2 id="editors-notes">Editor‚Äôs notes</h2>

<p>Hey friends! Here‚Äôs a new guitar lesson teaching you how to play ‚ÄúSimple Twist of Fate‚Äù, the classic from Bob Dylan‚Äôs 1975 album Blood on the Tracks. This is no doubt one of my favorite songs of all time, from an equally amazing album. This lesson teaches aims to make this song more accessible, teaching it in standard tuning, no capo, using chords in the key of E (which is slightly different than Dylan‚Äôs open-D-tuning, capo 2, Key of D arrangement). I‚Äôll explain all this in my video and PDF ‚Äì showing you the chords / progression / strumming, before offering two playthroughs using different strum patterns. I hope you enjoy!</p>

